					and products. However, all content is provided "as is" for informational purposes only.
					We make no guarantees about the completeness or accuracy of any information on the Site.
				</p>
				<p>
					Product recommendations reflect our honest opinions. Prices, availability, and product
					specifications may change without notice. Always verify current details with the retailer.
				</p>

				<h2>Affiliate Links and Third-Party Sites</h2>
				<p>
					The Site contains affiliate links to third-party websites, primarily Amazon.com. We are
					not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of any third-party sites. Your
					use of third-party sites is governed by their respective terms and policies.
				</p>
				<p>
					For details on our affiliate relationships, see our
					<a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
				</p>

				<h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
				<p>
					All original content on the Site — including text, images, graphics, videos, and logos —
					is owned by JayArr Coffee and protected by copyright law. The JayArr Coffee name and
					logo are our trademarks.
				</p>
				<p>
					You may share links to our content and quote brief excerpts with proper attribution.
					For any other use, please contact us.
				</p>

				<h2>User Conduct</h2>
				<p>
					If you interact with the Site through comments, forms, or other features, you agree to
					provide accurate information and to conduct yourself respectfully. We reserve the right
					to remove any content that is spam, abusive, or otherwise inappropriate.
				</p>

